& [SLMLMStudioSidecarAdapterContract] is the contract for LM Studio compatible sidecar exchange
  + [contract_uuid] is 33df65a2-0ffe-42f8-97eb-4cb5f4028b1a
  + [slice_id] is SLM-23
  + [status] is source_implemented_policy_gated

  & [Purpose] is to prepare an exchange layer without committing to live network execution
    = must: build an OpenAI-compatible chat request for LM Studio
    = must: serialize SidecarPromptEnvelope as machine-readable prompt content
    = must: require provider suggestions in the response contract
    = must: parse provider suggestions from a structured response body
    = must: avoid direct graph mutation
    - never: execute network calls until the runtime verification policy gate is resolved

  & [LMStudioRequest] is the OpenAI-compatible chat payload
    + [endpoint] defaults to http://127.0.0.1:1234/v1/chat/completions
    + [model] is adapter configuration
    + [messages] include system and user messages
    + [temperature] defaults low for deterministic evidence
    + [max_tokens] is adapter configuration
    + [stream] is false in v0

  & [LMStudioResponseParsing] is the source-only parser boundary
    + [input] is assistant message content containing JSON
    + [expected_json] includes provider_suggestions
    + [output] is Vec<ProviderSuggestion>
    = must: preserve provider provenance encoded in suggestions

  & [RuntimeProjection] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs LM Studio request and parser helpers
    + [status] is source_complete_policy_gated
